\begin_layout Subsection
\paragraph_spacing double
Rebalancing and Geometric Mean-CVaR
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\paragraph_spacing double
We demonstrated the optimal tradeoff between CVaR and return when comparing
 single period geometric optimization and multiple period (annual) rebalancing
 optimization for a three year simulation period.
 The resulting efficient frontiers are shown in Figures 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
