\change_unchanged
 portfolios in comparison to the rebalancing portfolios, especially at higher
 risk and return levels, must be considered in light of the use of a t-copula.
 
\change_inserted 0 1271632431
This can be visualized by overlaying the geometric mean-CVaR efficient frontier
 with the rebalancing mean-CVaR efficient frontier as seen in Figure 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
