\change_unchanged
 and rebalancing portfolios at lower risk and lower CVaR are very similar
 but quickly diverge as the risk and CVaR increase
\change_deleted 0 1271606885
s
\change_unchanged
.
 We believe this is because the t-copula is symmetric, so there exists a
 fat upper tail as well as a fat lower tail.
 In this case, 
\change_inserted 0 1271606747
geometric
\change_deleted 0 1271606747
